Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙裙飛起！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳在…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿黛的小褲褲為尾巴開了個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且是條條花紋 簡稱尾條褲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別起奇怪的名字！還有妳在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做自由研究的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由研究？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天學校不是布置了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是什麼內容都可以總之研究自己感興趣的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就在做內褲的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣也不能突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三條內褲 發現！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾妲是兜襠布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是…兜襠布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四條內褲！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾芙和可兒是 南瓜褲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫它Drawers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙一涉及到內褲就有超人般的行動力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 我對內褲可是認真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是學校的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看茱蒂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的可有點刺激喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是內褲？還是繩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在那種地方有金屬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它好像完全沒盡到內褲的作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊妮因為一直穿著這套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以下面沒穿任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 伊妮醬沒穿內褲囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 也不能說是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶點心來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我研究大家的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員沒穿內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都沒穿啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天放假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以內褲也放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一不小心把全部內褲都洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優諾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的緊身褲就是內褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 優柏可是緊內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用這麼奇怪的省略法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就是全部了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真火熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露天澡堂果然很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是我們男性包場的時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謔 真有開放感啊 直哉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧拉夫先生…全都看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謔謔謔 說什麼娘娘腔一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別遮遮掩掩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 給我看看你的內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是平角褲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧拉夫是褲衩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 直哉先生的內褲是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲已經研究夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 蘿黛在做什麼研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是蘿黛的自由研究？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是龍的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概快要孵化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日葉 公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦 爸爸 奧拉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋好像沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是巢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的家沒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…明明就快出生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼 明日葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了大家也脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘 內褲之家完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就暖和了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做個好孩子喔 內褲醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻小龍的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 這下我和蘿黛的自由研究都是以內褲為題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:19.79,title_3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\fs40\bord3\pos(600,380)}連鎖的平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾妲她看起來很心神不寧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她父親要來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就像是去見戀人一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是父親不如說是師父比較恰當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師 什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見啊 謝爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…老師 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀·雷金哈特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原王國軍的劍術教頭 撫養謝爾妲長大的養父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年僅16歲時就一個人戰勝了東國的惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20歲擔任教頭 後來因為養病而卸任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在遠離人世 在深山的道場中隱居
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 殿下與謝爾妲第一次相見是距今4年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時為了拜託燕雀做殿下的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造訪了他的住處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳還沒明白自己的劍是什麼呢 謝爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下已經決定不為王族做事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今在這山村教這孩子劍術就是我的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖然還是半桶水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:09:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過再過個幾年搞不好也能退治惡龍喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀殿下 有些事情想和妳談談
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在裡面慢慢談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來陪陪殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊 老師他沒有接受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男性的話我才不想要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師哪裡不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人…那女人就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只要強就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很強喔 對村裡的孩子王也從來沒輸過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是說這種低等級的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 從剛才開始就不討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為妳在對誰說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說妳是女的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓謝爾妲擔任護衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那孩子來說可能還早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得的確實是時候該讓她找個目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請務必…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂「保護他人」為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 謝爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好喝喔 變得拿手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是直哉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾妲的信裡經常出現你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我稍稍有些掛心 幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帥氣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連身為男生的我也緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像忘記了什麼重要的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後謝爾妲怎麼會為殿下所用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋 居然要在這種鄉下地方待一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄉下真是對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有溫泉 可是個好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和男人沒什麼區別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可是馬上就會變得搖啊搖啊的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種保證吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這內衣算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這個太緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很適合嗎 很可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…被人說可愛還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果化化妝的話也不會輸給貴族的小姐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 妳學劍道想做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如跟誰打架的時候能打贏之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 不如來做我的護衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保護像我這樣高貴的人物可是很值得自豪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這樣對我說也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 保護什麼的 我也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是野狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒見過這種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做妳的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妳的對手是我啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才從浴室那裡有什麼動靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾妲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父 我要成為能夠保護公主殿下的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}正中下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不過那之後才是真正辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個野丫頭從言行舉止到禮儀禮法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是完全沒有去學的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個出色的弟子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直直直直直直…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直哉親！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 只是舊病復發…嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊病?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}您沒事吧 血 血在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換了教頭不是因為病 而是因為跟男弟子出了醜聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}直哉 你看我這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:31.00,title_3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,600)\fs40\bord3\pos(256,161)}11年前的上劃線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下究竟去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是加冕典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會真的在這種時候消失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才反對梅爾契麗妲殿下繼位的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊格貝妲殿下和葛莉耶妲殿下都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之得趕快找到殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾契麗妲殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在這裡摸什麼魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳突然間幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾契殿下 回城堡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由不得您任性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾契麗妲殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每次都這樣 給我差不多一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在世界樹下面的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐 妳沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有魔力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐妳濕透了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不也濕透了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 我們家離的很近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直這個樣子的話會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裡是人界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還哎呢 現在可不是這麼悠閒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要魔力恢復了馬上就能回去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說人界的大氣裡幾乎是不含魔力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能吸精了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從人類身上幾乎感覺不到魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我把毛巾放這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有換的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也一起進來洗不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅爾契麗妲殿下 那孩子有好強的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想大姐姐會不會是妖精呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…那時候看起來就像是從光裡出現的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確 姐姐我啊 是森林裡的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是女王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失 失敬了 沒 沒有什麼像樣的招待…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話 一定很忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然還把您帶回家來 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我還不是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒打算成為女王 也沒想過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 大家不擔心妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正擔心我的人 都已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有兩個姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候經常一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該是她們其中一人…成為女王的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明關係那麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻受了周圍人的慫恿 相互爭奪起王位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐們都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道會變成這樣的話 不生為姐妹…不生在王族裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知其中緣由還問了妳這種傷心事 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為害大姐姐傷心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要抱住我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我哭的時候 媽媽會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:19:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這麼小的孩子安慰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 不過接下來的事都是發生夢裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟我正做著同一場夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一場夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:20:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種輕飄飄的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的 但有很快活的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 暖和的是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼舒服的夢還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加冕典禮 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:21:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想起來忘記問他的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是的 梅爾契陛下
